                     <hi rend="largeCaps">JOHN CURLE</hi> (46)</persName>, was indicted<rs id="t18580920-846-offence-1" type="offenceDescription">
                     <interp inst="t18580920-846-offence-1" type="offenceCategory" value="sexual"></interp>
